&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills&lt;br&gt;• Understanding of HIPAA and patient privacy regulations&lt;br&gt;• Computer proficiency and data entry accuracy&lt;br&gt;• Ability to multitask in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
